import React, { Component } from 'react'
import {Container,Col,Row,Tab,Nav,Sonnet,Card,Accordion,Button} from 'react-bootstrap'
import UseFiltersToggle from './UseFiltersToggle'
import { ProSidebar, Menu, MenuItem, SubMenu } from 'react-pro-sidebar';

export class SidePannel extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
                    <Col sm={2}>
                    <Tab.Container id="left-tabs-example" defaultActiveKey="first">
                    <Row>
                        <Col sm={8}>
                        <Nav variant="dark" className="flex-column">
                            <Nav.Item>
                            <Nav.Link eventKey="first">Upload</Nav.Link>
                            </Nav.Item>
                        </Nav>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                    </Tab.Container>
                    <hr/>
                    
                    <Accordion>
  <Card>
    <Card.Header>
      <Accordion.Toggle as={Button} variant="link" eventKey="0">
        My Researches
      </Accordion.Toggle>
    </Card.Header>
    <Accordion.Collapse eventKey="0">
      <Card.Body>
      <Tab.Container id="left-tabs-example" defaultActiveKey="first">
                    <Row>
                        <Col sm={10}>
                        <Nav variant="dark" className="flex-column">
                            <Nav.Item>
                            <Nav.Link eventKey="first">Completed</Nav.Link>
                            </Nav.Item>
                            <Nav.Item>
                                <Nav.Link eventKey="first">Pending</Nav.Link>
                            </Nav.Item>
                            <Nav.Item>
                                <Nav.Link eventKey="first">Collaborating</Nav.Link>
                            </Nav.Item>
                        </Nav>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                    </Tab.Container>
      </Card.Body>
    </Accordion.Collapse>
  </Card>
  <Card>
    <Card.Header>
      <Accordion.Toggle as={Button} variant="link" eventKey="1">
        Saved
      </Accordion.Toggle>
    </Card.Header>
    <Accordion.Collapse eventKey="1">
      <Card.Body>
      <Tab.Container id="left-tabs-example" defaultActiveKey="first">
                    <Row>
                        <Col sm={10}>
                        <Nav variant="dark" className="flex-column">
                            <Nav.Item>
                            <Nav.Link eventKey="first">Completed</Nav.Link>
                            </Nav.Item>
                            <Nav.Item>
                                <Nav.Link eventKey="first">Pending</Nav.Link>
                            </Nav.Item>
                        </Nav>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                    </Tab.Container>
      </Card.Body>
    </Accordion.Collapse>
  </Card>
</Accordion>
                    </Col>
        )
    }
}

export default SidePannel
